                span.b-realizationHead__span.b-realizationHead__span_position.
                    Investigationes demonstraverunt lectores
                    legere me lius quod ii legunt saepius.
                    Claritas est etiam processus dynamicus, qui sequitur mutationem
                    consuetudium.
            .b-ourWork
                img(src="images/realization/exampleOfWork/browser-left.png", alt="mobile adaptive").b-ourWork__mobile
                img(src="images/realization/exampleOfWork/browser-center.png", alt="slider example").b-ourWork__slider
                img(src="images/realization/exampleOfWork/browser-right.png", alt="grid example").b-ourWork__photo